SQL> /* 조인 */
SQL> --1. John 사원의 이름과 부서이름, 부서위치(city)
SQL> -- 오라클 조인
SQL> select e.first_name, d.department_name, l.city
  2  from employees e, departments d, locations l
  3  WHERE first_name='John'
  4  AND e.department_id=d.department_id
  5  AND d.location_id=l.location_id;

SQL> -- 안시 조인
SQL> select e.first_name, d.department_name, l.city
  2  from employees e
  3  JOIN departments d ON e.department_id=d.department_id
  4  JOIN locations l ON d.location_id=l.location_id
  5  WHERE first_name='John';

SQL> --2. 103번 사원의 사원번호, 이름, 급여, 매니저이름, 매니저 부서이름 (안시조인)
SQL> select e.employee_id, e.first_name, e.salary, m.first_name, d.department_name
  2  from employees e
  3  JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id=m.employee_id
  4  JOIN departments d ON m.department_id=d.department_id
  5  WHERE e.employee_id=103;

SQL> --3. 90번부서 사원들의 사번, 이름, 급여, 매니저이름, 매니저급여, 매니저부서이름
SQL> -- 오라클 조인
SQL> select e.employee_id, e.first_name, e.salary,
  2  	 m.first_name, m.salary, d.department_name
  3  from employees e, employees m, departments d
  4  where e.manager_id=m.employee_id(+)
  5  and m.department_id=d.department_id(+)
  6  and e.department_id=90;

SQL> -- 안시 조인
SQL> select e.employee_id, e.first_name, e.salary,
  2  	 m.first_name, m.salary, d.department_name
  3  from employees e
  4  LEFT JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id=m.employee_id
  5  LEFT JOIN departments d ON m.department_id=d.department_id
  6  where e.department_id=90;

SQL> --4. 103번사원이 근무하는 도시 (안시조인)
SQL> select e.employee_id, l.city
  2  from employees e
  3  JOIN departments d ON e.department_id=d.department_id
  4  JOIN locations l ON d.location_id=l.location_id
  5  where e.employee_id=103;

EMPLOYEE_ID CITY                                                                
----------- ------------------------------------------------------------        
        103 Southlake                                                           

SQL> 
SQL> --5. 사원번호가 103인사원의 부서위치(city)와 매니저의 직무이름(job_title) (안시조인)
SQL> select l.city "Department Location", j.job_title "Manager's Job"
  2  from employees e
  3  JOIN departments d ON e.department_id=d.department_id
  4  JOIN locations l ON d.location_id=l.location_id
  5  JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id=m.employee_id
  6  JOIN jobs j ON m.job_id=j.job_id
  7  where e.employee_id=103;

Department Location                                                             
------------------------------------------------------------                    
Manager's Job                                                                   
----------------------------------------------------------------------          
Southlake                                                                       
Administration Vice President                                                   
                                                                                

SQL> 
SQL> --6. 사원의 모든 정보를 조회하는 쿼리문
SQL> -- 사원의 부서번호는 부서이름으로, 직무아이디는 직무이름으로, 매니저아이디는 매니저이름으로
SQL> select e.employee_id, e.first_name, e.last_name, e.email, e.phone_number,
  2  	 e.hire_date, j.job_title, e.salary, e.commission_pct,
  3  	 m.first_name as manager_first_name, m.last_name as manager_last_name,
  4  	 d.department_name
  5  from employees e
  6  LEFT JOIN departments d on e.department_id=d.department_id
  7  JOIN jobs j ON e.job_id=j.job_id
  8  LEFT JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id=m.employee_id;
